'''麦尔·格里夫斯'''（{{lang-en|Melvyn Francis Greaves}}，{{bd|1941年|9月12日|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[癌症|癌症]][[生物学家|生物学家]]，伦敦[[癌癥研究院|癌癥研究院]]（ICR）教授<ref>{{cite web|title=Melvyn F Greaves|url=http://www.science-connections.com/profiles/greaves/melgreaves.html|publisher=www.science-connections.com|accessdate=21 December 2015|archive-date=2017-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170926174349/http://www.science-connections.com/profiles/greaves/melgreaves.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，知名于儿童[[白血病|白血病]]遗传与进化的研究<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.science-connections.com/video/node/29 |title=Interview with Melvin Greaves HPI Hamburg |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2011-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110910062909/http://www.science-connections.com/video/node/29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20151222122155/http://en.scientificcommons.org/melvyn_greaves </ref>，主要作品有《癌症——进化的遗产》（''Cancer: The Evolutionary Legacy''）等。
